data.enText: a person whose job is keeping a particular type of equipment or machinery in good condition

data.chText: （艺术、体育等的）技巧精湛者，精于技巧者
data.enText: a person who is very skilled at the technical aspects of an art, a sport, etc.

word_means: 技巧精湛者，精于技巧者
simple_means.memory_skill: techn 技术 + ician 人（精于某种学术或从事某种职业）→ 技术员

means: (艺术、体育等的)技巧精湛者，精于技巧者

tr: someone whose occupation involves training in a specific technical process
someone known for high skill in some intellectual or artistic technique

value.def: A technician is someone whose job involves skilled practical work with scientific equipment, for example in a laboratory.
A technician is someone who is very good at the detailed technical aspects of an activity.

example.ex: ...a versatile, veteran player, a superb technician.
example.tran: 技术全面、经验丰富、技巧娴熟的运动能手

rootsaffixes.indicate: = art, skill 技艺, 技术
rootsaffixes.title: techn(o)

techn 技艺，技术 + ician 人 → 技术员
techn 技艺，技术 + ique → 技术；技巧
techno 技艺，技术 + logy …学 → 技术（学）
